let _markdown = "\n\n## Complete ChIA-PET Analysis Workflow\n\nThis tutorial demonstrates a complete ChIA-PET data analysis pipeline using Chr3D.\n\n## Load Data\n\n```python\nfrom chr3d import ChIAPET\n\nchiapet = ChIAPET.from_bedpe(\"K562_CTCF_ChIAPET.bedpe\")\n```\n\n## Quality Control\n\n```python\nqc = chiapet.qc_report()\nprint(f\"Linker efficiency: {qc['linker_efficiency']:.1%}\")\nprint(f\"Cis/Trans ratio: {qc['cis_trans_ratio']:.2f}\")\n```\n\n## Filter Data\n\n```python\nfiltered = chiapet.filter_pets(min_pets=3)\nfiltered = filtered.filter_distance(min_distance=5000)\n```\n\n## Call Peaks and Loops\n\n```python\npeaks = filtered.call_peaks(genome=\"hg38\", qvalue=0.01)\nloops = filtered.call_loops(min_pets=3, peak_mode=True)\n```\n\n## Export Results\n\n```python\nloops.to_bedpe(\"loops.bedpe\")\npeaks.to_bed(\"peaks.bed\")\nchiapet.to_hic(\"output.hic\", resolution=5000)\n```\n\nSee [API reference](../api/chiapet) for detailed method documentation.\n";
